item.title: About
item.description: Dave (also: davidk) is the person behind open collector. This is mostly where I document things that don’t belong on other sites (thingiverse, forums), or are too long form for other mediums (like tweets). For the other stuff, here’s a list… 3D printables For most of the things i’ve built/designed to be printed, check out Thingiverse and YouMagine. The Github org, Collector3 also has version controlled copies. Most things will appear on Collector3 first since they don’t need full documentation + photos.
